These scripts are intended to convert the history of packages that
use a single tar ball to a git repo.

Create git repo from complete history:
./coall openSUSE:Factory foo
./importall

Checkout a single rev:
./co openSUSE:Factory foo 42

Import single rev to git:
./doimport 42

----
from /work/save ..
mkdir sources
cd sources
../linkoldpkg
cd ..
./importall
